           :   SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[id@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[false]
           :     VisibilityFilterExec: tables=[i]
           :       NestedLoopJoinExec: join_type=RightAnti, filter=pattern@3 = name@0 AND id@4 > id@1 OR pattern@3 = alt_name@2, projection=[ctid_0@0, id@2]
           :         CooperativeExec
           :           PgSearchScan: segments=1, query={"with_index":{"query":"all"}}
           :         CooperativeExec
