-- 18. Mixed native + UDF in one disjunction
-- =====================================================================
-- `upper()` is in the pg_catalog map → native; `md5()` is not →
-- `try_wrap_as_udf` wraps the md5 FuncExpr. EXPLAIN should show `upper`
